{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, the number of PPO epochs per PPO update is a critical parameter for PPO performance.",
    "Therefore, a limited grid search is executed on the three hyperparameters learning rate l r, PPO clipping value and PPO epochs n epochs.",
    "The three variants of each variable hyperparameter are listed in Table 1.",
    "Every parameter set tested is applied to ten simulation scenarios.",
    "Each scenario has the same parameters except for the random seed."
  ]
}